                      <li>Giatropoulos A., Balatsos G., Lytra I., Karras V., Koliopoulos G., Papachristos D. & Michaelakis A. (2024): Records of Aedes (Stegomyia) cretinus in Greece before and after the invasion of Aedes (Stegomyia) albopictus (Diptera: Culicidae). Eur. J. Entomol. 121: 199‚Äì205.</li>
                      <li>≈ûim≈üek F.M., Yava≈üoƒülu S.ƒ∞. (2023): Distribution of Aedes (Stegomyia) cretinus in T√ºrkiye. Turkiye Parazitol Derg. 47(2): 117‚Äì123. doi:10.4274/tpd.galenos.2023.72692.</li>
